title: Tom Holland, Zendaya, And Jacob Batalon Take A "Spider-Man: No Way Home" Quiz
author: BuzzFeed Celeb
description:
The biggest (and most emotional) Spider-Man movie is finally here, so to celebrate we had Tom Holland, Zendaya, and Jacob Batalon take a character quiz to find out which “Spider-Man: No Way Home” characters they really are. Is Tom really like Peter? Which MCU actors would they love to star in rom-coms with? Watch the video now and take the quiz for yourself too! https://www.buzzfeed.com/noradominick/spider-man-no-way-home-character-quiz
